type="local">positive</fr:link> elements of a lifted dcpo <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {L}{A}]]></fr:tex> are exactly the <fr:em>defined</fr:em> elements, i.e. those lying in the image of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[{A}\xrightarrow {{\eta }}{\mathsf {L}{A}}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
